![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1594230144556-5RPFSQWFAU865DFRT3AW/image-asset.jpeg)

Eric O'Grady is not your typical S.H.I.E.L.D. agent. He's lazy, aloof, and spends his days staring at a monitor in the surveillance room. His fellow agents seem more heroic, but O'Grady rather pick up chicks, sleep in and avoid responsibility at all costs. Unfortunately for our friend Eric, he comes into possession of a new and improved Ant-Man suit, and hijinx ensues. Join us as we talk about the most reluctant hero we have ever discussed: The IRREDEEMABLE Ant-Man

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](/comicbookclique/episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
